name: SAHASRA
description:
SAHASRA

This work is a visualization of a person's multiple personality. Starting from conflicting thoughts, conflicting voices from the same source. This proves that the human person works in complex and difficult ways to explain clearly. 

watercolor on cold press 300gsm
2192 × 2954 Pixel
